Join us here for a PREVIEW of our daily one-hour RUMBLE show. 
To continue watching the show in full, join me exclusively over on RUMBLE: https://bit.ly/SF533-live

Trump just announced that the U.S. will take control of Gaza—but what does that even mean? With Neil Oliver and Lara Logan, I break down the shockwaves of this declaration. Is it another off-the-cuff Trumpism, a calculated geopolitical move, or something deeper? We also expose the hidden hand behind USAID—has it been a front for the CIA all along? Plus, my candid conversation with OnlyFans creator Lily Phillips reveals the cultural impact of pornography and its intersection with technology. Don't miss this episode of *Stay Free*, where nothing is off-limits.
title: Trump in Gaza - a construction project? – SF533
